# Reference data of the implementation `splitmix64` in Fortran 2008 #

## How to compile ##

### Debug Mode ###

```console
cd build
cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=debug
make
```

### Release Mode ###

```console
cd build
cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=release
make
```
